name: complex_if_add_common_left_factor
section: control-if-arithmetic
args: cond:Bool common:Int a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: A common left addend can be lifted across an if expression.
law: (= (fuzz-add {common} (if {cond} {a} {b})) (if {cond} (fuzz-add {common} {a}) (fuzz-add {common} {b})))
